Module eu.daproject.evl

Package eu.daproject.evl.util

This package provides some common classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoundedLinkedHashMap<K,​V>
    Class defining a bounded linked hash map used to create default bounded caches.
    CacheFactory
    Helper class to create a bounded or unbounded cache.
    CacheItem
    The class holds the method handle and reflective method for the cache.
    ClassTuple
    Class representing a class tuple by encapsulating an array of Class.
    EmptyMap<V,​K>
    Empty map class used by the PredicateMethod1 and other predicate multimethods that cannot use a cache.
